    <subfield code="a">4pp Towards New Paradigms: Proceeding Of The Spanish Relativity Meeting 2011. AIP Conference Proceedings, Volume 1458, pp. 487-490 (2012). Published in AIP Conf.Proc. 1458 (2011) 487-490</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
